title: Fat Camp Curves by Aya Fukunishi
description:
Christa has lived her whole life locked in a love/hate relationship with chocolate. It just calls out to her, begging to be eaten, and she finds it impossible to resist.

Enough is enough, though. She'd love to keep her beautiful, curvy figure, and if it means she has to spend a week in the notoriously strict Willow Heights health resort that's a price she's willing to pay.

Three days in and she's consumed just 200 calories and worked out from dawn 'til dusk. Her hot, muscular personal trainer Ryan just won't let up on her...
... Until he decides she's earned a treat. 
Fat Camp Curves is a messy, sticky, gooey and juicy erotic story about one big, beautiful woman's love affair with a hot stud and a bar of melted milk chocolate. 

Genre: Erotic Romance
